  "detailed_description": "<h1>Feature List</h1><p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/015e8f7d62f436b67ab7e488a2f01f56.poster.avif?t=1760289724\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/015e8f7d62f436b67ab7e488a2f01f56.webm?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/015e8f7d62f436b67ab7e488a2f01f56.mp4?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span> </p><ul class=\"bb_ul\"><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Utilize a diverse selection of blocks to build anything: cars, trucks, boats, planes, trains, everything you can imagine is possible!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Action blocks bring your creations to life: wheels, motors, hinges, thrusters, sensors and even antigravity devices give a wide range of fun possibilities!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > An intuitive in-game scripting system allows anyone to program complicated contraptions and entire games quickly and easily!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Create, share, explore, and trade unique experiences and models with other players from all over the world!</p></li><li><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" > Build a car, design a course, publish the race and watch the world race for the fastest time!<br><br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline crossorigin=\"anonymous\" poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/f62697b3bd2d3b71757440f3ea4c4c3e.poster.avif?t=1760289724\" width=600 height=338 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/f62697b3bd2d3b71757440f3ea4c4c3e.webm?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"></video></span></p></li></ul></p><br><h1>About the Game</h1><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/67de743b5e8c803dab721630c4d740cc.poster.avif?t=1760289724\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/67de743b5e8c803dab721630c4d740cc.webm?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/67de743b5e8c803dab721630c4d740cc.mp4?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Blocksworld is a build-and-play system that brings the imaginative joy of toy blocks to your computer, allowing you to bring your digital creations to life! Build anything you can imagine with a diverse set of building blocks, colors, and textures, then program them to function with action commands. Cars, trucks, trains, airplanes, boats, submarines, space ships, robots, animals, dinosaurs, anything is possible!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/c168bafe86a050b3e043e0f4f5727a61.poster.avif?t=1760289724\" width=230 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/c168bafe86a050b3e043e0f4f5727a61.webm?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/c168bafe86a050b3e043e0f4f5727a61.mp4?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've created a world you're proud of, share it with other players in our community!  Let people from around the world interact with the experience you've created, and browse worlds built by others to find more inspiration yourself!  Watch as trends and memes rise and fall!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/2267e7a00285d426ed1b44c8130b0c5f.poster.avif?t=1760289724\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/2267e7a00285d426ed1b44c8130b0c5f.webm?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/2267e7a00285d426ed1b44c8130b0c5f.mp4?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you can imagine it, you can build it. <br> </p>",
  "about_the_game": "<p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/67de743b5e8c803dab721630c4d740cc.poster.avif?t=1760289724\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/67de743b5e8c803dab721630c4d740cc.webm?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/67de743b5e8c803dab721630c4d740cc.mp4?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>Blocksworld is a build-and-play system that brings the imaginative joy of toy blocks to your computer, allowing you to bring your digital creations to life! Build anything you can imagine with a diverse set of building blocks, colors, and textures, then program them to function with action commands. Cars, trucks, trains, airplanes, boats, submarines, space ships, robots, animals, dinosaurs, anything is possible!<br><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/c168bafe86a050b3e043e0f4f5727a61.poster.avif?t=1760289724\" width=230 height=156 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/c168bafe86a050b3e043e0f4f5727a61.webm?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/c168bafe86a050b3e043e0f4f5727a61.mp4?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span></p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" >Once you've created a world you're proud of, share it with other players in our community!  Let people from around the world interact with the experience you've created, and browse worlds built by others to find more inspiration yourself!  Watch as trends and memes rise and fall!</p><p class=\"bb_paragraph\" ><span class=\"bb_img_ctn\"><video class=\"bb_img\" autoplay muted loop playsinline poster=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/2267e7a00285d426ed1b44c8130b0c5f.poster.avif?t=1760289724\" width=300 height=168 ><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/2267e7a00285d426ed1b44c8130b0c5f.webm?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/webm; codecs=vp9\"><source src=\"https://shared.akamai.steamstatic.com/store_item_assets/steam/apps/642390/extras/2267e7a00285d426ed1b44c8130b0c5f.mp4?t=1760289724\" type=\"video/mp4\"></video></span><br>If you can imagine it, you can build it. <br> </p>",
